Package: ucursito
Version: 0.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, chromium-browser | google-chrome-stable, chromium-chromedriver | google-chrome-stable
Recommends: python3-selenium, python3-icalendar, python3-click, python3-requests
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/iaaaanb/ucursos-scraper
Description: U-Cursos scraper and calendar exporter
 Ucursito is a command-line tool to scrape and organize content from the
 U-Cursos university portal.
 .
 Features:
  - Download files from Material Docente, Novedades, and Tareas sections
  - Export calendar events (Controls and Tarea deadlines) to ICS format
  - Serve calendar via HTTP for live subscription in calendar apps
  - Automatic credential management with first-time setup
  - Smart file organization with course abbreviations
  - Selective section scraping with CLI flags
 .
 The package installs to /opt/ucursito and creates a 'ucursito' command
 that can be run from anywhere.
